data.description: HUGH PRICE ADJUSTMENT...Private and serine.  Less than 4 miles from downtown Saratoga but you feel like you are miles from anyone and in nature.  Trees surround the property with a year-round stream.  RV/boat parking area, parking area for guests.  Mountain living without the Hwy 17 beach traffic.  If you are looking for a well kept home with pool and deck, privacy, nature setting but yet minutes from town...you have found it.  Come take a look.
